# This repo is the PUBLIC GitHub Pages site (mrlerner/care).
# The erin-care folder also holds private source material (emails, .md drafts,
# clinical notes). To prevent any of that from being published by accident,
# we ignore EVERYTHING by default and explicitly allow only the published pages.
#
# To publish a NEW page: add a matching "!<filename>" line below, then commit.

*

!.gitignore
!index.html
!in-home-concierge-plan.html
!additional-resources.html
!care-team.html
!managed-hospital-admission.html
!motivation-best-practices.html
!neuroplasticity-approaches.html
!prioritized-tracking-docs.html
!stories-of-hope.html
!tracking-documents.html
